{"tid":1743834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［講比藍絲聽］民建聯賣港 出賣愛國愛港人","createTime":"2019-11-21T11:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T22:34:14.000Z","uid":18577,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f699eae255487475a286d86c65262be846dd85e9","tid":1743834,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"之前聽到民建聯會帶領大家去美領抗議原本好開心<br />\n重叫哂身邊藍絲個日朝早投完票就去join佢個遊行<br />\n我哋連國旗都準備好<br />\n點知依家民建聯fb出咗聲明黎強烈譴責<br />\n重話無講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我對民建聯真係好失望<br />\n原本全家都一心投佢<br />\n依家不了 覺得比佢呃咗<br />\n口講愛國愛港..原來都係假架<br />\n星期日投票..唔會投比依D出賣愛國愛港香港人嘅黨派<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zcT1M1q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzcT1M1q.jpg&h=3ab257b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0928d105164f8c6547ef07efb8288f2bc81c8d8","tid":1743834,"uid":18577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:36:01.000Z","msg":"民建聯不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da11714007cec6bfcf743d6d826905fd3893aa00","tid":1743834,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:36:16.000Z","msg":"我對民建聯好失望"},{"pid":"308a27fe26b8435e7e36cd20d2c6e102297a9b5c","tid":1743834,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:37:05.000Z","msg":"民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209da40099de441c722c1d79aa4fe22ff3df051c","tid":1743834,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:37:45.000Z","msg":"口講愛國愛港<br />\n身體最誠實 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/